data.description:
Beautiful Home in Patriots Landing! Sellers Hate to Leave! Stunning 3 bedroom 2 full bathroom home! This home is open and spacious So Roomy! This beautiful property offers a formal dining room and spacious office! Enjoy all the Amenities in Patriots Landing! The community features lakes to use non motorized boats, fishing, walking/jogging paths, club house, large zero entry pool with life guards, playgrounds! Easy commute to Richmond or Williamsburg. Restaurants, shopping, the new free standing emergency room! Starbucks, Arby's and Buc-ee's 
Coming Soon! New Fence and Irrigation! Yard is Bigger than the Fence Line!
